snippet.title: Johnny Depp Officially Buys Pirates Of The Caribbean Franchise...
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Officially Buys Pirates Of The Caribbean Franchise...
For many who are supporting Johnny Depp throughout his current "state of affairs" in regards to the court case that's STILL going on with him and his ex-wife Amber Heard, the big "payoff" if you will isn't just that Amber Heard could be revealed to be a major liar, but that they would get to see Depp on the big screen again. Especially in the role of Captain Jack Sparrow potentially should he be brought back to the Pirates of the Caribbean franchise like many want. But there are all sorts of signs that even if Depp is cleared...Disney won't bring him back. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at what might just happen with Captain Jack Sparrow and the Pirates franchise as a whole should things go the way they have been recently. Do you think that Disney will just kill off Jack or write him out of the franchise so they never have to navigate those turbulent waters again? Or do you think if Depp is cleared they'll welcome him back with open arms? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
